This had to be in the top 3 lines I heard while I was pregnant. I have been traveling since I was very very young so I knew I wanted that exact lifestyle for all my kids. Not only can you absolutely travel with kids but in my eyes it is absolutely more enjoyable. Kids like everything in life must be trained. Nevertheless, if you want a good traveler train him/her to be a good traveler. Key point here START EM YOUNG. Dre knows no better than just acting the right way when it’s time to take another flight. Another key point you’d be very surprised how well kids mold/adapt into your lifestyle.
